"Number of columns in the output.  If `N` is not specified, a square array is "
"returned (``N = len(x)``)."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../../../../../.conda/lib/python3.13/site-packages/numpy/ma/extras.py:docstring
#: of numpy.ma.extras.vander:22
